---
title: Share-Style Sticky Korean Fried Chicken with Garlic Rice, Pickled Radish & Slaw
description: Brace yourself for a flavour explosion! This sticky Korean fried chicken brings the sweet, savoury, crispy vibes, served up with garlicky rice, crunchy slaw, tangy pickled radish, and a swoosh of creamy garlic aioli. It’s a choose-your-own-adventure kind of meal, so pile your plate high with all your favourites!

